    "view": {
      "representation": "view",
      "value": "<p><strong>RenderManStudio_Lighting_v01.hip</strong><br/><br/>This scene is the end of the Solaris pipeline and is where the <em>$HIP/usd/Layout/RenderManStudio_Layout_v1.usda</em> file is loaded it.  <br/><br/>As you can see from the stage, a number of lights have been set up to get you started.  The <em>edit </em>node is there for final layout tweaks and a close and wide camera has also been added.<br/><br/>For extra realism, a procedural fog setup is also included and the thickness and fog height can be easily controlled via the 2 promoted parameters located on the <em>sopcreate_Volume</em> node<br/><br/><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544642691/RenderManStudio_Lighting_Solaris.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433105336&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544642691/RenderManStudio_Lighting_Solaris.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433105336&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544642703\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"RenderManStudio_Lighting_Solaris.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544642691\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"a7990e07-ea11-409e-837f-7c030e7ff04b\" data-media-type=\"file\"></span><br/><br/><br/>There are two cameras already set up.</p><p>/RenderManStudio/CAM/RenderCam_wide_35mm<br/><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544642691/RenderManStudio_Wide_Lighting.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433105336&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544642691/RenderManStudio_Wide_Lighting.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433105336&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544642706\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"RenderManStudio_Wide_Lighting.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544642691\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"1eca8478-8ac8-4698-8851-8df1fa1f2177\" data-media-type=\"file\"></span><br/><br/>/RenderManStudio/CAM/RenderCam_Close_85mm<br/><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544642691/RenderManStudio_Close_Lighting.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433105336&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544642691/RenderManStudio_Close_Lighting.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433105336&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544642709\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"RenderManStudio_Close_Lighting.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544642691\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"18dd1b04-5a65-4585-b22a-a8620985f05f\" data-media-type=\"file\"></span><br/><br/><br/>The scene is all setup for you to render out both the wide and close cameras ... we've even setup denoising!</p>"
    }
